               =20
                <div class=3D"term-desc-contents">
                  <div class=3D"term-desc-scrollable">
                    <div class=3D"paragraph">In OpenAPI the components obje=
ct is a storage for reusable components. Components inside this object can =
be referenced from other parts of the documentation. This makes it a good s=
torage for any descriptions that pop up frequently, including path paramete=
rs, various schemas, and request body objects. This also includes security =
schemes if your API uses authentication.</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
               =20
                  <div class=3D"term-desc-contents" style=3D"display:none;"=
>
                    <div class=3D"term-desc-scrollable">
                      <div><pre class=3D"normal"><code class=3D"highlight y=
